name: The aftermath
description:
When mankind has disappeared and the machines have fallen, the flies will rise. BOTGOD, the lord of the flies itself, knew about that a long time ago and created zillions of these eager companions to found a new world in the aftermath of the past.

ORIGINAL RESOLUTION: 2.510 × 1.824 × 400
TOOLS USED: pencil, copic marker, crayons on paper, Photoshop
